description: AIFarm, Ltd., a development stage company, develops a proprietary growing system that designs and builds custom biodomes worldwide. Its biodomes are used for commercial agricultural concerns, as well as small local producers. The company was formerly known as Eco Energy Tech Asia, Ltd. and changed its name to AIFarm, Ltd. in January 2020. AIFarm, Ltd. was founded in 2012 and is based in Kowloon, Hong Kong.
